OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy with showers,
OL,6,Fperhaps some longer spells of rain at
OL,7,Ftimes. Some bright or sunny spells
OL,8,Fbreaking through in the afternoon.
OL,9,FStrong southeasterly winds across
OL,10,FShetland at first.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FVariable amounts of cloud and
OL,13,Fa few showers this evening. Then
OL,14,Fthickening cloud will bring some
OL,15,Foccasional light rain from the
OL,16,Fsouthwest in the early hours.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
