OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FCloudy with occasional rain or
OL,6,Fdrizzle, this turning more persistent
OL,7,Ffor a time in the afternoon. Drier
OL,8,Facross Orkney later. Fresh southerly
OL,9,Fwinds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FOften
OL,12,Fcloudy with showers over the weekend.
OL,13,FFewer showers on Monday. Fresh to
OL,14,Fstrong west or southwesterly winds on
OL,15,FSaturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
